  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Nimal Siripala de Silva resigned following the request of the President",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President has ordered the initiation of detailed investigations into the allegation made by the Leader of the Opposition in Parliament yesterday (05) regarding the exchange of money reported to have taken place between the Ministry of Civil Aviation and a private company.",
        "According to a statement issued by the Presidential Media Unit, Nimal Siripala de Silva will temporarily step down from the post of the Ministry of Ports, Containers and Aviation Services until the investigations are completed."
      ],
